# Title: Potentially Suspicious Execution From Tmp Folder
# Author: Joseliyo Sanchez, @Joseliyo_Jstnk
# Date: 2023-06-02
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects a potentially suspicious execution of a process located in the '/tmp/' folder
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1036
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/process_creation/proc_creation_lnx_susp_execution_tmp_folder.yml

Image="/tmp/*" NOT Image="*/usr/bin/nextcloud"